{"pageProps":{"post":{"creator":"Evelina Judeikyte","title":"My top five newsletters for data communication","link":"https://www.theplot.media/p/top-five-newsletters","pubDate":"Thu, 07 Jul 2022 22:11:40 GMT","content:encoded":"<p>It&#8217;s 9am in Paris. The sun is already shining and people are getting ready for work. I&#8217;ve poured myself a cup of coffee and, still in pyjamas, I open up my inbox on the phone. No, I&#8217;m not about to read my business emails. Not yet. Instead, I navigate to the folder that contains a dozen newsletters I receive every week. I click on one of them and slowly get lost in the world of data, design and communication.</p><p>This is what my morning routine looks like a few times a week. Reading regular content from professionals across a mix of fields keeps me informed, inspired and even entertained. That&#8217;s why in today&#8217;s edition of The Plot I&#8217;ll talk about my five favourite newsletters &#8212; hopefully they&#8217;ll inspire you too!</p><h2>1. quantum of sollazzo </h2><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link is-viewable-img image2\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bb0711c-89c7-49df-8714-57b3aa54b01d_1138x646.gif\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bb0711c-89c7-49df-8714-57b3aa54b01d_1138x646.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bb0711c-89c7-49df-8714-57b3aa54b01d_1138x646.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bb0711c-89c7-49df-8714-57b3aa54b01d_1138x646.gif 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bb0711c-89c7-49df-8714-57b3aa54b01d_1138x646.gif 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bb0711c-89c7-49df-8714-57b3aa54b01d_1138x646.gif\" width=\"1138\" height=\"646\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3bb0711c-89c7-49df-8714-57b3aa54b01d_1138x646.gif&quot;,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:646,&quot;width&quot;:1138,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:23414788,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/gif&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bb0711c-89c7-49df-8714-57b3aa54b01d_1138x646.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bb0711c-89c7-49df-8714-57b3aa54b01d_1138x646.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bb0711c-89c7-49df-8714-57b3aa54b01d_1138x646.gif 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bb0711c-89c7-49df-8714-57b3aa54b01d_1138x646.gif 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#FFFFFF\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" y1=\"3\" x2=\"14\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"21\" x2=\"10\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class=\"image-caption\">A glimpse into <em>quantum of sollazzo</em>, a data newsletter by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/puntofisso\">Giuseppe Sollazzo</a></figcaption></figure></div><p><em>Quantum of sollazzo</em> is a data newsletter by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/puntofisso\">Giuseppe Sollazzo</a>. What I love most about it is that the newsletter is always chock full of links and references to the latest data design and journalism pieces. By the time I open the email, I will have typically seen at least some of the projects it showcases. But there are always at least a couple I wouldn&#8217;t have stumbled upon by myself. If you&#8217;re looking to keep up with the latest work in the field, I strongly recommend you read <em>quantum of sollazzo</em>.</p><h5>Subscribe to <a href=\"https://buttondown.email/puntofisso\">quantum of sollazzo</a></h5><h2>2. Notes from the equator </h2><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link is-viewable-img image2\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffbb97813-9745-4983-bcdc-c9e24385cf8a_1138x646.gif\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffbb97813-9745-4983-bcdc-c9e24385cf8a_1138x646.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffbb97813-9745-4983-bcdc-c9e24385cf8a_1138x646.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffbb97813-9745-4983-bcdc-c9e24385cf8a_1138x646.gif 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffbb97813-9745-4983-bcdc-c9e24385cf8a_1138x646.gif 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffbb97813-9745-4983-bcdc-c9e24385cf8a_1138x646.gif\" width=\"1138\" height=\"646\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/fbb97813-9745-4983-bcdc-c9e24385cf8a_1138x646.gif&quot;,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:646,&quot;width&quot;:1138,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:23786501,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/gif&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffbb97813-9745-4983-bcdc-c9e24385cf8a_1138x646.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffbb97813-9745-4983-bcdc-c9e24385cf8a_1138x646.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffbb97813-9745-4983-bcdc-c9e24385cf8a_1138x646.gif 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffbb97813-9745-4983-bcdc-c9e24385cf8a_1138x646.gif 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#FFFFFF\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" y1=\"3\" x2=\"14\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"21\" x2=\"10\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class=\"image-caption\">A glimpse into <em>notes from the equator</em>, a data storytelling newsletter by <a href=\"https://kontinentalist.com/\">Kontinentalist</a></figcaption></figure></div><p><em>Notes from the equator</em> is published by the team at <a href=\"https://kontinentalist.com/\">Kontinentalist</a>, a data storytelling agency based in Singapore. I believe the team takes turns to write the newsletter, so that each time the readers are presented with a new perspective. It typically starts with some reflections on an important matter &#8212; for example, <a href=\"https://mailchi.mp/kontinentalist.com/of-things-that-flow-and-connect?e=5fc5af4b6ahttps://mailchi.mp/kontinentalist.com/of-things-that-flow-and-connect?e=5fc5af4b6a\">infrastructure, trade and money flows</a>. Then, the writers dive deeper into the topic by introducing a featured data story and sharing all the delicious details on how they developed and designed it. If you&#8217;re looking for inspiration from outside of the Western world, this newsletter is for you!</p><h5>Subscribe to <a href=\"https://kontinentalist.us12.list-manage.com/subscribe?u=2280632ef90de9d24551a7997&amp;id=57892f324d\">notes from the equator</a></h5><h2>3. FILWD </h2><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link is-viewable-img image2\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F71bffb87-ef13-4846-baad-1ef7bbfb3029_1138x646.gif\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F71bffb87-ef13-4846-baad-1ef7bbfb3029_1138x646.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F71bffb87-ef13-4846-baad-1ef7bbfb3029_1138x646.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F71bffb87-ef13-4846-baad-1ef7bbfb3029_1138x646.gif 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F71bffb87-ef13-4846-baad-1ef7bbfb3029_1138x646.gif 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F71bffb87-ef13-4846-baad-1ef7bbfb3029_1138x646.gif\" width=\"1138\" height=\"646\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/71bffb87-ef13-4846-baad-1ef7bbfb3029_1138x646.gif&quot;,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:646,&quot;width&quot;:1138,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:11763164,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/gif&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F71bffb87-ef13-4846-baad-1ef7bbfb3029_1138x646.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F71bffb87-ef13-4846-baad-1ef7bbfb3029_1138x646.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F71bffb87-ef13-4846-baad-1ef7bbfb3029_1138x646.gif 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F71bffb87-ef13-4846-baad-1ef7bbfb3029_1138x646.gif 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#FFFFFF\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" y1=\"3\" x2=\"14\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"21\" x2=\"10\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class=\"image-caption\">A glimpse into <em>FILWD</em>, a data viusalisation newsletter by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/FILWD\">Enrico Bertini</a></figcaption></figure></div><p><em>FILWD</em>, which stands for <em>Fell In Love With Data</em>, is a letter by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/FILWD\">Enrico Bertini</a>. Contrary to what we typically call a &#8220;newsletter&#8221;, Enrico sends out reflections on the data visualisation field inspired by his teachings at the New York and Northeastern universities. He raises questions such as: Is it OK to guide the reader in a visualisation? What would a theory of data visualisation look like? What mental models do we use in data visualisation? Reading FILWD will encourage you to think more deeply about data visualisation and its research.</p><h5>Subscribe to <a href=\"https://filwd.substack.com/\">FILWD</a></h5><h2>4. Dense Discovery</h2><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link is-viewable-img image2\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F21a089a1-f63b-4e6d-8f35-c67659214805_1138x646.gif\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F21a089a1-f63b-4e6d-8f35-c67659214805_1138x646.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F21a089a1-f63b-4e6d-8f35-c67659214805_1138x646.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-b